OL,3,CSand collected from D-Day beach
OL,4,Creturned by grandson in 80-year promise
OL,6,F"He told me he'd been in D-Day," Dan
OL,7,Fsaid. "In fact he's the inspiration
OL,8,Fand the reason for why I joined the
OL,9,Farmy and I had a long and successful
OL,10,Fcareer serving as well and it was all
OL,11,Fdown to him and the stories he told
OL,12,Fme."
OL,14,FHe added: "I still find it quite sad
OL,15,Fthat a lot of our younger generation
OL,16,Fdon't know what D-Day is, they don't
OL,17,Funderstand the significance of it.
OL,19,F"In the world we live in today we need
OL,20,Fto educate them, and I'm hoping to do
OL,21,Fthat as well."
