OL,6,FDan is an ambassador of the charity
OL,7,Fwalking with the wounded, and together
OL,8,Fwith supporters is taking part in a
OL,9,F150km hike across all five D-Day
OL,10,Flanding sites.
OL,12,FAnt Middleton, a former Special
OL,13,FServices Operator and star of SAS Who
OL,14,FDares Wins, is one of those walking.
